1. *Milione* ljudi živi u ovom gradu. (Millions of people live in this city.)
2. Država je potrošila *milione* evra na obnovu puta. (The state spent millions of euros on road renovation.)
3. Njegov novac broji se u *milionima*. (His money is counted in millions.)
4. Zarađuje *milione* svake godine. (He earns millions every year.)
5. *Milioni* ljudi su izgubili posao tokom pandemije. (Millions of people have lost their jobs during the pandemic.)
6. Njegova firma ima prihod od *milion* dolara godišnje. (His company has an annual revenue of a million dollars.)
7. Svetsko prvenstvo gledaće *milioni* ljudi širom sveta. (Millions of people around the world will watch the World Cup.)
8. On je uložio *milione* u novu tehnologiju. (He invested millions in new technology.)
9. Cene nekretnina u ovom gradu dostižu *milione*. (Real estate prices in this city reach millions.)
10. *Milioni* ljudi su potpisali peticiju za zaštitu životne sredine. (Millions of people have signed a petition for environmental protection.)